sequenceDiagram
    accTitle: User Journey Sequence
    accDescr: Typical user flow from landing to viewing resume and portfolio
    
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant Router
    participant Home
    participant Resume
    participant Portfolio
    participant Data
    
    User->>Browser: Visit website
    Browser->>Router: Load /
    Router->>Home: Render Home page
    Home->>Data: Import resumeData.profile
    Data-->>Home: Profile info
    Home-->>Browser: Display Hero + Journey
    Browser-->>User: Show landing page
    
    User->>Browser: Click "Check Resume"
    Browser->>Router: Navigate to /resume
    Router->>Resume: Render Resume page
    Resume->>Data: Import resumeData
    Data-->>Resume: Experience, Education, Skills
    Resume-->>Browser: Display timeline + cards
    Browser-->>User: Show resume
    
    User->>Browser: Click "View Portfolio"
    Browser->>Router: Navigate to /portfolio
    Router->>Portfolio: Render Portfolio page
    Portfolio-->>Browser: Display project grid
    Browser-->>User: Show portfolio
    
    Note over User,Portfolio: All data is static<br/>No API calls needed
